> Political Obama cites sacrifices made by fallen firefighters President Barack Obama pauses as he speaks during the National Fallen Firefighters Memorial Service at Mount St. Mary’s University’s Knott Athletic Recreation Convocation Complex (ARCC) in Emmitsburg, Md., Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, to honor 84 firefighters who died in the line of duty in 2014 and three firefighters who died in previous years. (AP Photo/Carolyn Kaster) 
